  "subject": "Chore: Update RTD and tox config for ubuntu-24.04",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Update RTD and tox config for ubuntu-24.04\n\nUpdate .readthedocs.yaml to ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13, replacing the\ndeprecated ubuntu-20.04 image and EOL Python 3.8.\n\nSwitch tox.ini from remote upper-constraints URL to a local\netc/upper-constraints.onap.txt file, avoiding build failures when\ngit.onap.org returns HTTP 500 errors. Update basepython to 3.13.\n\nDrop the mistune==0.8.4 pin in docs/requirements-docs.txt; it is\nincompatible with the rest of the modern Sphinx tool chain under\nPython 3.13 and is not referenced directly by the cert-service docs.\nAdd the six dependency so sphinxcontrib-swaggerdoc can still be\nimported as a Sphinx extension under Python 3.13.\n\nFix broken Jenkins URLs in docs/sections/build.rst so the\ndocs-linkcheck job passes.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: I76855fc5ecc969fa412c5d000339020b07f93546\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
